data.text:
Afonso XII De Borbon

Afonso XII De was born on November 28th, 1857 in Madrid, Spain. He died at the age of 27 on November 25th, 1885 in El Pardo, Madrid, Spain.

Maria De Las Mercedes D' Orleans

Maria De Las Mercedes D' was born on June 24th, 1860 in Madrid, Spain. She died at the age of 18 on June 26th, 1878 in Madrid, Spain.
